{"tid":270650,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【李華華搶先睇】孫柏文開網台 講明係「燈」","createTime":"2017-06-04T12:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T13:15:48.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f94a26853df3a1d35d79ebb04d1178f736fc934","tid":270650,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170604/large/1496578756_0856.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170604%2Flarge%2F1496578756_0856.png&h=35658011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出名係「燈神」嘅股評人孫柏文最近有新搞作，走去開網台，佢都好識自嘲，節目名就係叫做「大明燈」。<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文呢個節目，上星期啱啱開波，每日有兩段片，唔派冧巴，主要講財金熱話，好似早前有沽空機構狙擊瑞聲科技(2018)，佢就評論一番，仲好大膽咁咀咒「股王」騰訊(700)，估遲早有沽空機構做佢世界㖭呀。不過孫柏文有燈神之稱，大家又唔使太上心嘅。<br />\n<br />\n華華睇過其中兩段片，片長約7、8分鐘，喺今日網絡資訊爆炸嘅年代，略嫌太長，除非觀眾係孫柏文嘅忠實粉絲，否則聽兩三分鐘就想走。<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文就話，睇過用戶睇片嘅趨勢，facebook用戶一般只能接受15秒長嘅片，而Youtube用戶比較有耐性，10分鐘都得，所以佢用Youtube做平台。佢家陣一邊做節目，剪埋片，一邊搵廣告同贊助商，希望試到一個營運模式。<br />\n<br />\n問佢是咪想轉型做財經KOL，佢反而即刻為財經KOL定義，指財經KOL唔係計有幾多人like、幾多follower之類，而係要睇KOL是咪能夠推郁資產價格，即係一講某個冧巴，某個冧巴就會升或跌，而佢唔屬意喺節目畀冧巴，只係想做自己想睇嘅節目啫，將來可能仿傚美國個別talk show嘅模式做節目㖭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56783702&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56783702%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170604&d=TEndGv67gCBVqEOXLRsCRm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2a67667b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56783702%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170604&h=c991e542\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56783702&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170604</a>"},{"pid":"a35a2f192026da1df3976369d9b5e44b38eb5cfe","tid":270650,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"扮師父？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f249ed56acc386749a0dca0718ef22cd0587121f","tid":270650,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮師父？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n燈冇得學，呢條友燈力係有但唔係師父嗰皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8f2ae231bfc9c0ad7d5014f2bd519560de0c5b","tid":270650,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扮師父？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n燈冇得學，呢條友燈力係有但唔係師父嗰皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果次幫師父睇風水，佢個水水水命格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 注定"},{"pid":"aefeb4d70d329ec689f15ab011b76e36d6d764b1","tid":270650,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170604/large/1496578756_0856.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170604%2Flarge%2F1496578756_0856.png&h=35658011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出名係「燈神」嘅股評人孫柏文最近有新搞作，走去開網台，佢都好識自嘲，節目名就係叫做「大明燈」。<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文呢個節目，上星期啱啱開波，每日有兩段片，唔派冧巴，主要講財金熱話，好似早前有沽空機構狙擊瑞聲科技(2018)，佢就評論一番，仲好大膽咁咀咒「股王」騰訊(700)，估遲早有沽空機構做佢世界㖭呀。不過孫柏文有燈神之稱，大家又唔使太上心嘅。<br />\n<br />\n華華睇過其中兩段片，片長約7、8分鐘，喺今日網絡資訊爆炸嘅年代，略嫌太長，除非觀眾係孫柏文嘅忠實粉絲，否則聽兩三分鐘就想走。<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文就話，睇過用戶睇片嘅趨勢，facebook用戶一般只能接受15秒長嘅片，而Youtube用戶比較有耐性，10分鐘都得，所以佢用Youtube做平台。佢家陣一邊做節目，剪埋片，一邊搵廣告同贊助商，希望試到一個營運模式。<br />\n<br />\n問佢是咪想轉型做財經KOL，佢反而即刻為財經KOL定義，指財經KOL唔係計有幾多人like、幾多follower之類，而係要睇KOL是咪能夠推郁資產價格，即係一講某個冧巴，某個冧巴就會升或跌，而佢唔屬意喺節目畀冧巴，只係想做自己想睇嘅節目啫，將來可能仿傚美國個別talk show嘅模式做節目㖭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56783702&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56783702%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170604&d=TEndGv67gCBVqEOXLRsCRm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2a67667b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56783702%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170604&h=c991e542\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56783702&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170604</a></blockquote><br />\n白銀隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}